result.name: Kin Kee Fast Food

reviews.text: If you want to try hk style noodle soup, this a a great place. You can choose the soup base spicy level.  The staff are usually helpful with non-cantonese speakers. Their food portion is decent. Current min charge per person is 35$
Love this place delicious quick and easy. Great flavours. Spicy sauce was perfect. Will definitely come gain.
I would say the food is on par. Its easy to order. There is a order sheet on the table. You just have yo fill it and give it to the staffs. Strong AC is a big plus.

When I came here late night, most of their dishes are sold out already, very disappointed on their arrangements.
The food here is ok, but the soup of the cart noodle is no good.  Although staffs here are firendly, but very disappointed on their food.  Price here is acceptable, and seatings here are packed, but in acceptable level

此麵店有段感人故事，多年前，呀堅身染絕症，生前願望想開一間車仔麵店，但事以願諱，未能實現就此去也，堅太傷心過後，有日想起老公的生前諱願，當然，以她一人之力是唔夠，她就常試吹雞，找佢老公生前最好的朋友，点知，大家一拍即合，就咁，堅記車仔麵就在西貢開業，而堅太盡最大努力，希望將堅記做到最好，講番間麵店，食物做得唔錯，以車仔麵來講，唔咁講數一數二，但都可以數三數四，而價錢略為貴咗少許，如去開西貢行行遠足等，又要醫肚，不妨試試，而堅太多數都會在舖頭
